		<h2 class="dash-trailing">This is Repose.</h2>
		<p>It is common to experience anxiety. Whether the cause is trying to meet an important deadline or preparing for an interview, these stresses typically subside at the conclusion of the event. However when the cause of these symptoms is unknown, the feeling of stress can escalate to a state of panic. In these moments, find Repose in your pocket to help lay your anxieties to rest.</p>
